	<h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
	<br>
	<h2>General</h2>
	<h3>What is Infinitory?</h3>
	<h4>Infinitory is a lab inventory and member management system. It gives labs the ability to build a real-time inventory of their most expensive reagents and devices. Automated real time notices are sent to members whenever their reagents are running low, expiring soon or when their devices break or are repaired.</h4>

	<h3>Who can use Infinitory?</h3>
	<h4>Any scientific lab or institute conducting basic research.</h4>

	<br>
